2:T6d4,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Levity better than Rossum?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Levity scores 7.0 overall while Rossum scores 7.0. Levity is best for document processing and email classification, while Rossum excels for enterprises and logistics."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Levity or Rossum?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Levity starts at $49/mo and Rossum starts at Custom.   Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Levity to Rossum?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Levity and Rossum support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Levity vs Rossum?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Levity holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Rossum has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 5/10. Users praise Levity for train custom ai classifiers without code and Rossum for high accuracy on structured documents."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Levity or Rossum?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Rossum for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Levity remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize train custom ai classifiers without code. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"compare-header","children":["$","div",null,{"classN